_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-wheel-detail-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101834/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_front-w