-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent.jpg 1000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/06101822/Scope-Cycling-prototype-lightweight-carbon-climbers-wheels_disc-brake-tubeless-at-Tour-de-France_Team-DSM_photo-by-Kristof-Ramon_Kramon_dark-descent-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-264118\">©kramon</figcaption></figure><p>Scope hasn’t yet confirmed that any new prototype wheels are in development after the release of their <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/16/scope-all-road-slots-3-gravel-ready-carbon-wheelsets-between-updated-road-off-road/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">updated Race</a> line, the new <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/07/01/scope-sport-carbon-road-wheels/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">lower-cost Sport</a> line, or whether these may simply be one of their existing wheels without logos. They’ve only confirmed that Scope &amp; Team DSM have been “working together for a while now” with the goal of further developing their wheel offerings.</p><p>But if DSM are testing out Scope prototype wheels at the Tour, we’d expect that they are close to, if not ready for production. While the Tour de France is a good proving ground, most teams wouldn’t risk racing anything they aren’t already confident in. So, consumer versions of new race-ready carbon wheels may be coming soon…</p><p><a href=\"https://www.scopecycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>ScopeCycling.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"5e544ac2185decc2e00c6ff28bbf7c10a4142d87b06f60f85d2d6bdd868acd4b","category":"Cycling"}